{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}I couldn't find my backpack.{\r}

519
01:03:15,630 --> 01:03:17,530
哦，不，不，不。那留在这里。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Oh, no, no, no. That stays here.{\r}

520
01:03:18,630 --> 01:03:20,200
我想向人们展示。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}I wanna show people.{\r}

521
01:03:20,330 --> 01:03:22,400
让我们等一会儿，好吗？
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Let's wait a while on that, okay?{\r}

522
01:03:22,530 --> 01:03:23,930
好。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Okay.{\r}

523
01:03:33,680 --> 01:03:35,110
你从哪里得到的？
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Where did you get those?{\r}

524
01:03:35,240 --> 01:03:37,980
我以为是你做的。我喜欢他们。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}I thought you made them. I like them.{\r}

525
01:03:38,110 --> 01:03:40,050
看起来像你和我。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Looks like you and me.{\r}

526
01:03:50,860 --> 01:03:53,860
栖息地是否一直在您的房间里？
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Has the habitat been in your room the whole time?{\r}

527
01:03:54,760 --> 01:03:56,070
嗯嗯。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Mm-hmm.{\r}

528
01:04:13,580 --> 01:04:14,980
你在干什么？
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}What are you doing?{\r}

529
01:04:24,630 --> 01:04:25,890
加油。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Come on.{\r}

530
01:04:29,970 --> 01:04:32,270
放学后待在室内，除非爸爸
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Stay inside after school unless Daddy{\r}

531
01:04:32,570 --> 01:04:37,070
或者我在这里，好吗？不要和其他人一起去，不管他们说什么。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}or I are here, okay? Don't go with anyone else, no matter what they say.{\r}

532
01:05:02,800 --> 01:05:04,000
这是关于什么的？
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}What's this about?{\r}

533
01:05:04,130 --> 01:05:05,430
只是感觉像。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Just felt like it.{\r}

534
01:05:05,670 --> 01:05:08,270
放学后可以接金盏花吗？
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Can you pick Marigold up after school?{\r}

535
01:05:08,400 --> 01:05:10,640
答案是肯定的。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Of course.{\r}

536
01:05:11,370 --> 01:05:12,370
为什么？
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Why?{\r}

537
01:05:13,840 --> 01:05:17,110
我必须做点什么。我不能告诉你它是什么。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}I have to do something. I can't tell you what it is.{\r}

538
01:05:23,350 --> 01:05:25,190
这是怎么回事，海伦娜？
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}What's going on, Helena?{\r}

539
01:05:26,660 --> 01:05:30,330
我知道我没有给你任何理由......
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}I know I haven't given you any reason to...{\r}

540
01:05:31,860 --> 01:05:33,400
请相信我。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}please trust me.{\r}

541
01:05:34,630 --> 01:05:36,270
我回来后会给你打电话。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}I'll call you when I get back.{\r}

542
01:05:37,170 --> 01:05:38,600
从哪里回来？
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Back from where?{\r}

543
01:05:40,170 --> 01:05:41,600
最后一个秘密，斯蒂芬。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Last secret, Stephen.{\r}

544
01:05:42,510 --> 01:05:44,040
承诺。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Promise.{\r}

545
01:06:04,290 --> 01:06:06,500
你和玛丽救了我。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}You and Mari rescued me.{\r}

546
01:08:10,920 --> 01:08:12,860
我可以随心所欲地称呼它吗？
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}I can call it anything I want?{\r}

547
01:08:12,990 --> 01:08:15,730
这是你的。我把它给了你。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}It's yours. I gave it to you.{\r}

548
01:08:19,800 --> 01:08:21,130
我的名字
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}I name it{\r}

549
01:08:21,970 --> 01:08:23,530
海伦娜瀑布。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Helena Falls.{\r}

550
01:10:29,320 --> 01:10:31,260
你好，小影子。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Hello, Little Shadow.{\r}

551
01:11:15,740 --> 01:11:17,640
我们去散散步吧。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Let's go for a walk.{\r}

552
01:11:36,060 --> 01:11:37,460
你怎么找到我的？
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}How did you find me?{\r}

553
01:11:37,590 --> 01:11:39,660
我从来没有失去过你，小影子。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}I never lost you, Little Shadow.{\r}

554
01:11:51,440 --> 01:11:53,310
我想念那种味道。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}I miss that smell.{\r}

555
01:11:56,440 --> 01:11:57,880
还有味道。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}And the taste.{\r}

556
01:12:01,620 --> 01:12:02,850
给我那个。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Gimme that.{\r}

557
01:12:15,260 --> 01:12:16,800
我最喜欢的刀。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}My favorite knife.{\r}

558
01:12:39,060 --> 01:12:41,520
我们曾经在这里露营，你还记得吗？
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}We used to come camping up here, you remember?{\r}

559
01:12:42,490 --> 01:12:45,290
我们整个夏天都会在这里躺着。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}We'd lay out here all summer long.{\r}

560
01:12:45,430 --> 01:12:46,730
仰望天空，
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Look up at the sky,{\r}

561
01:12:46,930 --> 01:12:48,600
看看谁能数出最多的流星。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}see who could count the most shooting stars.{\r}

562
01:12:49,530 --> 01:12:51,530
我曾经作弊和数飞机。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}I used to cheat and count airplanes.{\r}

563
01:12:55,200 --> 01:12:58,910
你知道我一直都活着，不是吗？
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}You knew I was alive the whole time, didn't you?{\r}

564
01:12:59,710 --> 01:13:01,640
我不知道这怎么可能。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}I didn't know how it was possible.{\r}

565
01:13:02,610 --> 01:13:05,050
直到我看到一只三足土狼。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Not until I saw a three-legged coyote.{\r}

566
01:13:06,650 --> 01:13:08,780
为了自由而牺牲了自己的腿。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Sacrificed its own leg for freedom.{\r}

567
01:13:08,920 --> 01:13:11,290
就像你牺牲了你的牙齿一样。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Like you sacrificed your teeth.{\r}

568
01:13:11,420 --> 01:13:13,460
啊。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Ah.{\r}

569
01:13:13,590 --> 01:13:15,690
可能不会通过体检，
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Probably won't pass a medical exam,{\r}

570
01:13:15,830 --> 01:13:17,990
但它为你赢得了你需要的时间。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}but it bought you the time you needed.{\r}

571
01:13:19,630 --> 01:13:21,400
你做了一些挖掘。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}You did some digging.{\r}

572
01:13:22,060 --> 01:13:23,670
干的好。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Well done.{\r}

573
01:13:28,910 --> 01:13:31,440
你没有告诉别人你的理论吗？
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}You didn't tell anyone else your theory?{\r}

574
01:13:33,410 --> 01:13:34,810
你？
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Did you?{\r}

575
01:13:40,020 --> 01:13:42,050
真希望你带上了金盏花。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Wish you'd brought Marigold.{\r}

576
01:13:43,420 --> 01:13:45,150
跟我说说我的孙女吧。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Tell me about my granddaughter.{\r}

577
01:13:45,290 --> 01:13:49,160
我不这么认为。你已经对她了解得够多了。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}I don't think so. You know enough about her already.{\r}

578
01:13:52,730 --> 01:13:54,560
好吧，我不得不看一眼。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Well, I had to take a peek.{\r}

579
01:13:56,700 --> 01:13:58,770
你从来没带她来看我。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}You never brought her to visit me.{\r}

580
01:14:00,570 --> 01:14:02,200
你根本没有来看我。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}You didn't visit me at all.{\r}

581
01:14:06,640 --> 01:14:07,880
来吧，小影子。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Come on, Little Shadow.{\r}

582
01:14:08,010 --> 01:14:09,780
我想向你展示一些东西。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}I want to show you something.{\r}

583
01:14:12,480 --> 01:14:15,790
你知道，金盏花长得很像她。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}You know, Marigold looks like her.{\r}

584
01:14:16,390 --> 01:14:17,390
令堂。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Your mother.{\r}

585
01:14:18,250 --> 01:14:20,760
我敢打赌，她和我们一样喜欢水。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}I bet she loves the water as much as we do.{\r}

586
01:14:25,660 --> 01:14:27,700
那就是带我们越过边界。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}That's to take us across the border.{\r}

587
01:14:28,330 --> 01:14:29,670
我们三个人。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}The three of us.{\r}

588
01:14:30,670 --> 01:14:32,770
对加拿大来说，我们可以再次成为一家人。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}To Canada, we can be a family again.{\r}

589
01:14:33,640 --> 01:14:34,670
我有一个家庭。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}I have a family.{\r}

590
01:14:34,800 --> 01:14:36,170
你有一个女儿。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}You have a daughter.{\r}

591
01:14:36,310 --> 01:14:37,610
还有一个丈夫。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}And a husband.{\r}

592
01:14:38,370 --> 01:14:39,680
我们共同建立了生活。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}We've built a life together.{\r}

593
01:14:40,710 --> 01:14:42,180
你对这种生活满意吗？
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Are you happy with that life?{\r}

594
01:14:44,510 --> 01:14:45,780
并非总是如此。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Not always.{\r}

595
01:14:45,980 --> 01:14:48,020
你有没有回想过那是什么样子的？
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Do you ever think back to what it was like{\r}

596
01:14:48,480 --> 01:14:49,590
我们什么时候住在这里？
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}when we lived here?{\r}

597
01:14:49,850 --> 01:14:53,490
-我愿意。 -我们可以再来一次。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}-I do. -We can have it all again.{\r}

598
01:14:56,090 --> 01:14:59,060
我记得你四岁的时候，
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}I remember when you were four years old,{\r}

599
01:14:59,200 --> 01:15:01,030
你可以闭上眼睛
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}you could shut your eyes{\r}

600
01:15:02,230 --> 01:15:06,340
你从水声中知道你在哪里，
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}and you knew where you were from the sound of the water,{\r}

601
01:15:06,470 --> 01:15:09,340
从树木的气味中，
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}from the smell of the trees,{\r}

602
01:15:09,470 --> 01:15:14,040
以及脚下地面的感觉。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}and the feel of the ground beneath your feet.{\r}

603
01:15:14,180 --> 01:15:15,880
这就像魔术一样。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}It was like magic.{\r}

604
01:15:19,280 --> 01:15:21,050
这就是我们的归属。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}This is where we belong.{\r}

605
01:15:21,180 --> 01:15:23,020
这是我们的家。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}It's our home.{\r}

606
01:15:23,520 --> 01:15:24,990
我们在这里的生活
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Our life here{\r}

607
01:15:26,060 --> 01:15:27,190
很完美。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}was perfect.{\r}

608
01:15:40,340 --> 01:15:41,440
不！
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}No!{\r}

609
01:15:46,410 --> 01:15:47,740
不！
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}No!{\r}

610
01:15:51,980 --> 01:15:54,350
你不要再从我身边逃跑了！
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Don't you ever run away from me again!{\r}

611
01:15:54,850 --> 01:15:56,650
好？你听到了吗？
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Okay? You hear me?{\r}

612
01:16:01,160 --> 01:16:02,220
我没有--
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}I wasn't--{\r}

613
01:16:10,100 --> 01:16:11,130
完善？
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Perfect?{\r}

614
01:16:12,800 --> 01:16:14,040
不是为了我妈妈。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Not for my mother.{\r}

615
01:16:14,600 --> 01:16:16,140
嗯，本来可以的。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Well, it could've been.{\r}

616
01:16:16,270 --> 01:16:17,370
如何？
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}How?{\r}

617
01:16:18,270 --> 01:16:21,710
-你绑架了她。-不。我们一起逃跑了。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}-You kidnapped her. -No. We ran away together.{\r}

618
01:16:21,840 --> 01:16:25,250
这只是她决定离开时说的话。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}That's just something she said when she decided to leave.{\r}

619
01:16:25,380 --> 01:16:28,020
-你开枪打死了那个人。 -我试图撞到引擎。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}-You shot that man. -I was trying to hit the engine.{\r}

620
01:16:28,150 --> 01:16:29,620
你永远不会错过。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}You never would have missed.{\r}

621
01:16:30,690 --> 01:16:32,320
我错过了。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}I missed.{\r}

622
01:16:32,460 --> 01:16:35,690
你听过一堆关于我的故事。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}You've been told a bunch of stories about me.{\r}

623
01:16:35,830 --> 01:16:40,030
他们不是真的。我从来都不是沼泽之王，直到他们说我是。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}They're not true. I never was the Marsh King, until they said I was.{\r}

624
01:16:42,630 --> 01:16:44,630
我知道这一点，我们很开心。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}I know this, we were happy.{\r}

625
01:16:45,400 --> 01:16:46,840
你很开心。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}You were happy.{\r}

626
01:16:48,400 --> 01:16:51,310
我只想说，把金盏花带过来，让她自己看看。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}All I'm saying, bring Marigold, let her see for herself.{\r}

627
01:16:51,440 --> 01:16:52,910
我不能那样做。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}I can't do that.{\r}

628
01:16:54,110 --> 01:16:55,280
我不会的。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}I won't.{\r}

629
01:16:56,850 --> 01:16:58,680
对不起。这就是它结束的地方。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}I'm sorry. This is where it ends.{\r}

630
01:17:00,820 --> 01:17:02,890
我不应该来这里。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}I shouldn't have come here.{\r}

631
01:17:05,890 --> 01:17:07,760
我很高兴我做到了。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}I'm glad I did.{\r}

632
01:17:11,830 --> 01:17:14,660
现在我必须回家和家人团聚。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Now I have to go home to my family.{\r}

633
01:17:15,400 --> 01:17:18,370
请不要再靠近他们了。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Please don't come near them again.{\r}

634
01:17:19,240 --> 01:17:22,000
-它不需要是这样的。-确实如此。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}-It doesn't need to be like this. -It does.{\r}

635
01:17:26,810 --> 01:17:28,210
好。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Okay.{\r}

636
01:17:28,710 --> 01:17:29,810
好。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Okay.{\r}

637
01:17:29,950 --> 01:17:31,810
我理解。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}I understand.{\r}

638
01:17:39,920 --> 01:17:41,820
你永远是我的小影子。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}You'll always be my Little Shadow.{\r}

639
01:17:45,760 --> 01:17:47,260
我得走了。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}I have to go.{\r}

640
01:18:24,200 --> 01:18:25,230
克拉克？
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Clark?{\r}

641
01:18:26,570 --> 01:18:29,810
-你在这里干什么？-可以问你同样的事情。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}-What are you doing here? -Could ask you the same thing.{\r}

642
01:18:29,940 --> 01:18:32,170
斯蒂芬打电话给我。他很担心。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Stephen called me. He was worried.{\r}

643
01:18:32,310 --> 01:18:35,240
我只是在你说的话之后有一种预感。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}And I just had a hunch after what you said.{\r}

644
01:18:36,680 --> 01:18:40,020
-他在这里吗？-我们回去吧。我会在路上告诉你的。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}-Is he here? -Let's go back. I'll tell you on the way.{\r}

645
01:18:40,150 --> 01:18:43,050
海伦娜，他在这里吗？
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Helena, was he here?{\r}

646
01:18:44,720 --> 01:18:45,960
但他已经走了。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}But he's gone.{\r}

647
01:19:00,940 --> 01:19:02,670
克拉克。克拉克。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Clark. Clark.{\r}

648
01:19:02,810 --> 01:19:05,810
克拉克。天啊。天啊。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Clark. Oh, God. Oh, God.{\r}

649
01:19:08,680 --> 01:19:10,480
克拉克，看看我，好吗？
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Clark, look at me, okay?{\r}

650
01:19:10,610 --> 01:19:12,350
克拉克。克拉克，和我在一起。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Clark. Clark, stay with me.{\r}

651
01:19:12,680 --> 01:19:15,750
你告诉他你要来这里？不，我什么也没说。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}You told him you were coming here? No, I didn't say anything.{\r}

652
01:19:16,090 --> 01:19:17,520
请看我。
{\fs10\1c&H2DA6EE&}Please, look at me.{\r}

653
